We’re keeping it classic here with a skillet-fried aged rib eye steak, butter, fresh herbs and garlic, roasted potatoes and garlic mayonnaise. Aren’t these some of the best pleasures in life? Recipe by Spier. Tip: Slide the potatoes into the oven, then make the aioli, and lastly the steak – this way it will be ready to serve at the same time. For the steak: (serves 2) For the hasselback potatoes: For the aioli: Prepare the potatoes: Make the aioli: Prepare the steak: Spier wines can be tasted and purchased at the farm in Stellenbosch, and are widely available in stores and online at shop.spier.co.za.